      "span_text": "In one case, a 40-year-old woman presented to an orthopaedic department with a Google image of a dislocated ankle which she attempted to pass as her own radiograph. [CITATION_1] Factitious disorder was soon suspected based on various inconsistencies between the radiograph and the woman's own presentation.",
